1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to the Nebraska Housing Agency Act; to amend
2 section 71-1572, Revised Statutes Cumulative Supplement, 2024; to
3 provide duties for certain housing agencies relating to bed bugs; to
4 harmonize provisions; and to repeal the original section.
5 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
